Wenger: &quot;We were a team who was really dominant and had a good structure in the game. We stuck together when Stoke made it rough for us.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger on reaching the top four: &quot;I don't know, let's focus to make 72 [points]. The team at the moment looks strong and solid.&quot;

Ars&egrave;ne Wenger: &quot;We were a bit unlucky because they scored their goal with a hand... we reacted well and won convincingly.&quot;<br />
<br />
 Ars&egrave;ne Wenger: &quot;All we can do is win our matches, continue our streak and hope that the others fail to overcome their obstacles.&quot;
